General.Name: Instabank ASA
General.Description: Instabank ASA provides various banking products and services in Norway. The company accepts deposits; and offers consumer and secured loans, refinance, and credit cards, as well as loans for vehicles and boats. It also provides payment, car, and dental health insurance products. Instabank ASA was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Oslo, Norway.
